---
import LayoutDefault from "~/layouts/LayoutDefault.astro";
---

<LayoutDefault>

<section class="about-page">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="page-title">About Me</h1>

    <p class="intro">
      Welcome to my InfoSec blog!
    </p>

    <p class="line-height-relaxed">
      I'm a <strong>Computer Science student</strong> with a passion for cybersecurity, currently aiming toward a <strong>Master’s degree in IT Security</strong>. This blog serves as a personal space to capture every milestone in my journey, allowing me to revise key concepts easily, and share what I’ve learned with others in the field.
    </p>

    <p>
      I’m actively pursuing the following certifications:
    </p>

    <ul class="certifications-list">
      <li><strong>CompTIA Security+ (Sec+)</strong></li>
      <li><strong>Certified Penetration Testing Specialist (HTB CPTS)</strong></li>
      <li><strong>Certified Defensive Security Analyst (HTB CDSA)</strong></li>
    </ul>

    <p class="line-height-relaxed">
      Alongside certifications, I regularly solve <strong>HackTheBox machines</strong> to hone my pentesting skills, and use <strong>HackTheBox Sherlock</strong> to sharpen my defensive strategies.
    </p>

    <h4 class="section-title">Let’s Connect!</h4>

    <p class="line-height-relaxed">
      I invite you to join me on this journey by discussing topics, sharing insights, or even collaborating! Feel free to provide feedback, share your thoughts, or contribute through pull requests. This blog is not just about my learning—it’s about fostering a community of curious and driven individuals.
    </p>

    <p class="closing">
      Thanks for stopping by, and I hope you find my posts helpful!
    </p>

    <p class="signature">
      — <strong>Thanh Nguyen</strong>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding: 40px 0;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .certifications-list {
    margin: 20px 0;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  .section-title {
    margin: 30px 0 20px;
    font-size: 2rem;
  }

  .closing {
    margin-top: 30px;
    font-style: italic;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .signature {
    text-align: right;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
</style>

</LayoutDefault>
